messages.message:
Brian
I'd volunteer btw, but you never texted me back about dinner   and I'm not goth.

...dinner... oh yea! I did forget! Sorry lol.
I don't necessarily need anyone goth, just one who's open minded. But I'm picky, and you and I don't know eachother well enough yet.

Brian
True story.  What do you mean by open minded?  I mean, obviously I can assume what you mean, but I'm curious to know what your example of open minded is.  I pretty much like to do everything with friends.  I like going out, I went to a bunch of electronic shows this year, I like to stay in an watch movies, I like to cook, I like to go camping, I love skiing.

Brian
I am pretty picky too, but I'd like someone to hang out with.

See, that's awesome! I like all that stuffs. What I mostly mean by open minded is - I obviously have several "goth" friends, and plenty of ones who aren't, but I don't need anyone bashing on either of the groups. I have such a variety of friends because I am so open minded. Y'know?

Yea we can hang out. Probably not this week, I'm oober busy. Bleh.

Brian
Haha, I get it.  I was just teasing anyways.  Everyone I've met so far seems pretty interesting.
